191 (2) Findings showing that the child was
192 represented by counsel;
193 (3) Findings showing that the hearing was
194 held in the presence of the child and his or her
195 counsel; and
196 (4) Findings showing the reasons
197 underlying the court's decision to transfer
198 jurisdiction.
