121 the tax authorized pursuant to this section
122 shall be deposited in a special trust fund and
123 shall be used solely for providing a juvenile
124 detention facility for children coming within
125 the provisions of this chapter for so long as
126 the tax shall remain in effect.
127 (4) Once the tax authorized by this
128 section is abolished or terminated by any means,
129 all funds remaining in the special trust fund
