132 (24) "Tier II offender":
133 (a) An individual who has been adjudicated for a tier
134 II offense; or
135 (b) Any offender who is adjudicated for an offense
136 comparable to a tier I offense or failure to register
137 offense under section 589.425 or comparable out-of-state
138 failure to register offense and who is already required to
