18 published on the internet in accordance with this section.
1 [43.650.] 589.411. 1. The Missouri state highway
2 patrol shall[, subject to appropriation,] maintain a web
3 page on the internet which shall be open to the public and
4 shall include a registered sexual offender search capability.
5 2. Except as provided in subsections 4 and 5 of this
6 section, the registered sexual offender search shall make it
7 possible for any person using the internet to search for and
